// Inline SVG content for the HandiBowls lockup + mark.
//
// Source: Claude Design delivery (2026-05-07 "HandiBowls Brand
// Assets" — see /design bundle chat9.md). The .svg files live in
// public/brand/handibowls/ for direct serving; these inner-content
// strings exist so HandiBowlsWordmark / HandiBowlsMark can embed
// the SVG directly into the DOM. Inline embedding is required —
// the lockup and wordmark use <text font-family="Barlow Condensed">,
// which only resolves when the SVG is part of the host document
// (an <img src=".svg"> sandbox would not see the next/font load).
//
// Each constant is everything between <svg ...> and </svg> in the
// source file. Consumers wrap in their own <svg viewBox=...> and
// pass the string via dangerouslySetInnerHTML.

